---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="Our story, instructors, and contact information for Kinney Karate in St. Petersburg, FL.">

<div class="belt"><span class="w"></span><span class="y"></span><span class="g"></span><span class="b"></span><span class="k"></span></div>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
    <h1 class="cond">About Kinney Karate</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <div class="story" id="story">
      <p class="kick">Our Story</p>
      <div class="story-body">
        <p>Kinney Karate was founded in 1969 by Soke David Kinney. Over the decades the school grew from a single class into a multi-location program serving students of all ages across St. Petersburg and Pinellas County.</p>
        <p>Soke Kinney began his martial arts journey in the Korean art of Tang Soo Do, and expanded his studies to include Aikido, Ju Jitsu, and Modern Arnis — eventually earning the rank of 9th degree black belt. He dedicated his life to sharing these arts with his community, believing that martial arts training builds not just physical skill but character, discipline, and resilience.</p>
        <p>Today, Kinney Karate continues under the leadership of Soke Dai Susan Serota and a team of experienced instructors who carry on Soke Kinney's legacy. Classes are held at St. Petersburg Recreation Centers, making high-quality martial arts training accessible and affordable to everyone.</p>
        <p>We also partner with <a href="https://balancemartialarts.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--red)">Balance Martial Arts &amp; Gaming</a> in Pinellas Park for advanced training and specialty programs — including our unique Kinney Karate Dungeons &amp; Dragons program that combines the values of martial arts with the imagination and teamwork of tabletop gaming.</p>
        <p>Over 55 years and counting, Kinney Karate has trained hundreds of black belts, tournament champions, and — most importantly — better people. Many of our students have been with us for decades. We are proud to now teach the children and grandchildren of our original members.</p>
        <p>We are a family — and we'd love to have you join us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Instructors -->
    <div class="instructors" id="instructors">
      <p class="kick">Our Instructors</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-soft);margin-bottom:24px;font-size:14px">Our instructor team brings decades of combined martial arts experience across multiple disciplines.</p>
      <div class="instructor-grid">
        {[
          {
            name: 'Susan Serota',
            title: 'Soke Dai Grand Master, Ph.D.',
            rank: '9th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Susan.png',
            bio: 'Susan Serota holds a 9th degree black belt and serves as Soke Dai (successor to the founder) of Kinney Karate. She has been training and teaching under Soke Kinney for decades and leads the school with the same dedication to tradition, community, and personal growth that has defined Kinney Karate for over 55 years.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Seth Koehler',
            title: 'Grand Master',
            rank: '8th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Seth.png',
            bio: 'Seth Koehler holds an 8th degree black belt and has been an integral part of the Kinney Karate instructor team for many years. His depth of knowledge across Tang Soo Do, Aikido, Ju Jitsu, and Modern Arnis makes him a versatile and highly skilled teacher.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Richard Serota',
            title: 'Senior Master Instructor',
            rank: '7th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Richy.png',
            bio: 'Richard Serota holds a 7th degree black belt and brings decades of martial arts experience to his teaching. He is a cornerstone of the Kinney Karate community and embodies the school\'s values of discipline, respect, and continuous improvement.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Jackie Prats',
            title: 'Master Instructor',
            rank: '6th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Jackie.png',
            bio: 'Jackie Prats holds a 6th degree black belt and brings energy and dedication to every class. Jackie helps students of all levels grow in technique, confidence, and character.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Stavro Liginos',
            title: 'Master Instructor',
            rank: '5th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Stavro.png',
            bio: 'Stavro Liginos holds a 5th degree black belt and has been teaching at Kinney Karate for many years. His enthusiasm for the martial arts and his students makes his classes both challenging and rewarding.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Sonja Leone',
            title: 'Master Instructor',
            rank: '4th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Sonja.png',
            bio: 'Sonja Leone holds a 4th degree black belt. She brings energy and precision to her classes, helping students of all ages develop technique, confidence, and a love for the martial arts.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Kelly Bonyata',
            title: 'Master Instructor',
            rank: '4th Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Kelly2.png',
            bio: 'Kelly Bonyata holds a 4th degree black belt. Her patient and encouraging teaching style is especially effective with younger students and beginners, helping them build a strong foundation in the martial arts.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Tatsiana Haverkamp',
            title: 'Instructor',
            rank: '3rd Degree Black Belt',
            photo: '/instructors/Tats.png',
            bio: 'Tatsiana Haverkamp holds a 3rd degree black belt. Her commitment to the martial arts and her students makes her a valued member of the Kinney Karate teaching team.',
          },
        ].map(i => (
          <div class="instructor-card">
            <div class="instructor-avatar">
              <img src={i.photo} alt={i.name} width="72" height="72" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
            </div>
            <h3>{i.name}</h3>
            <p class="title-label">{i.title}</p>
            <p class="rank-label">{i.rank}</p>
            <p class="bio">{i.bio}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Memorial Fund -->
    <div class="memorial" id="memorial">
      <p class="kick">Soke Kinney Memorial Fund</p>
      <div class="memorial-card">
        <div class="memorial-photos">
          <img src="/Michael-student-remastered.png" alt="Grand Master Soke Michael Kinney" class="memorial-photo" />
          <img src="/michael-w-kid-sm.png" alt="Grand Master Soke Michael Kinney with student" class="memorial-photo" />
        </div>
        <h2>In Memory of Grand Master Soke Michael Kinney</h2>
        <p>The Soke Kinney Memorial Fund is a nonprofit established to honor the legacy of Kinney Karate's founder. The fund supports martial arts education and community programs in St. Petersburg.</p>
        <p>The Memorial Fund operates independently of Kinney Karate retail. Donations and fund activities are handled separately — visit <a href="https://www.sokekinneymemorial.org/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--red)">sokekinneymemorial.org</a> for more information.</p>
        <p><em>The Soke Kinney Memorial patch is available in the <a href="/store" style="color:var(--red)">school store</a> — a small way to carry his legacy.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <div class="contact" id="contact">
      <p class="kick">Contact</p>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Questions about classes, enrollment, or the school? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
        <p class="contact-direct">Call us: <a href="tel:+17276860864">727-686-0864</a></p>
        <form class="contact-form" method="POST" action="/api/contact">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-name">Your name</label>
            <input type="text" id="cf-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-email">Email address</label>
            <input type="email" id="cf-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cf-msg">Message</label>
            <textarea id="cf-msg" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <!-- Turnstile widget — site key set via env -->
          <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAAD3XYraMXD0jlcAv"></div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
.page-hero { background:var(--ink);color:var(--text-invert);padding:48px 0 40px; }
.page-hero h1 { font-size:52px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px; }
.pad { padding:48px 0; }

.story, .instructors, .memorial, .contact { margin-bottom:56px; }
.instructor-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:16px;
}
@media (max-width:900px) { .instructor-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); } }
@media (max-width:640px) { .instructor-grid { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); } }
.story-body p { font-size:15px;color:var(--text-soft);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.8;max-width:720px; }

.instructor-card {
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);background:#fff;padding:24px;text-align:center;
}
.instructor-avatar {
  width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--line);margin:0 auto 14px;overflow:hidden;
}
.instructor-avatar img {
  width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top center;display:block;
}
.instructor-card h3 { font-weight:700;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:3px; }
.title-label { font-size:13px;color:var(--text-soft);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:3px; }
.rank-label { font-size:12px;color:var(--red);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:10px; }
.bio { font-size:13px;color:var(--text-soft);line-height:1.6; }

.memorial-card, .contact-card {
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r-lg);background:#fff;padding:28px;
}
.memorial-photos {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.memorial-photo {
  width: 180px;
  height: 220px;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: top;
  border-radius: var(--r);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.memorial-card h2, .contact-card h2 { font-weight:700;font-size:22px;margin-bottom:14px; }
.memorial-card p { font-size:14px;color:var(--text-soft);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.7; }

.contact-direct { font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px; }
.contact-direct a { color:var(--red);font-weight:600; }
.contact-form { margin-top:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;max-width:520px; }
.field { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px; }
.field label { font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text); }
.field input, .field textarea {
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:9px 12px;
  font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:14px;color:var(--text);
  background:#fff;width:100%;
}
.field input:focus, .field textarea:focus {
  outline:2px solid var(--red);outline-offset:0;border-color:transparent;
}
</style>

<!-- Turnstile script — loads asynchronously -->
<script src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js" async defer></script>
